		<div data-secondsdelay="" id="iudsrw">
		  <span data-text="text" data-secondsdelay="" id="i447gp">These Terms of Service shall be governed by and construed in accordance with the laws of the State of Arizona without giving effect to any choice or conflict of law provision or rule (whether of the State of Arizona or any other jurisdiction).</span>
